cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SI, cs.CE, cs.DC 

The paper uses machine learning models (multilayer perceptron and multiple linear regression) to predict energy consumption based on demographic and economic parameters. This falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also deals with data analysis and modeling, which could be categorized under computational engineering (cs.CE) and data structures and algorithms (cs.DC). Finally, the paper deals with societal impact (energy consumption) and sustainability, which could be categorized under social and information sciences (cs.SI).
